Hi There,

During Open Hours, you should be able to use the function "Switch Secondary Sections" without removing yourself from the waitlist. Please email me with any questions/issues. 

Update to Students: Telebears was giving this student the wrong information about her waitlist position on the secondary sections. If you notice something odd, like being bumped from 3rd or 4th on a secondary section waitlist to 26th, please email me so we can look into it.
